channel.title: If you were to meet any popular music star, who would it be?
channel.description: Hey guys! There are a lot of celebrity music stars out there! I want to know, who would you desire to meet? If you would rather vote then I will figure maybe even a contest! My music star I would like to meet is either Alan Walker or Jon Bellion.

item.title: If you were to meet any popular music star, who would it be?
item.dc:creator: El1011
item.description:
lmao oof. i remember that.

But i will say that Alan Walker probably definately has a ghost producer judging by the Alone walkthough. The guy was clueless on pretty much every aspect of the track and didnt seem to really know the plugins n software he used.

I dont think he can’t produce (he had to get signed somehow lol), just that he is forced to let others produce the whole track because of his contract.
Some people have noted some subtle differences between Fade [before signed] and Faded [after getting signed]. Faded was probably remixed/remastered by some professionals to have a more professional/clean sound.
